  <h1>About MeaFar</h1>
  
  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>MeaFar is transforming education through intelligent technology. We design customized EduTech solutions that empower schools and universities to improve student outcomes, streamline operations, and embrace data-driven decision-making.</p>
  
  <h2>Founded by Educators, Built for Educators</h2>
  <p>What sets MeaFar apart is our pedigree. We're not consultants observing education from the outside — we're founders and leaders who have shaped educational institutions. We understand the challenges, constraints, and opportunities that schools and universities face.</p>
  
